    "faq_item_1_q": "Was ist TestaScreen?",
    "faq_item_1_a": "TestaScreen bietet kostenlose, professionelle Bildschirmtest- und Display-Kalibrierungswerkzeuge. Unsere Tools helfen Ihnen, Dead Pixels zu erkennen, Farbgenauigkeit zu testen, Helligkeit und Kontrast zu prüfen und mehr.",
    "faq_item_2_q": "Muss ich etwas installieren?",
    "faq_item_2_a": "Nein! Alle TestaScreen-Tools werden direkt in Ihrem Webbrowser ausgeführt. Besuchen Sie einfach unsere Website und beginnen Sie sofort zu testen.",
    "faq_item_3_q": "Ist es wirklich kostenlos?",
    "faq_item_3_a": "Ja, völlig kostenlos. Wir glauben, dass professionelle Tools für alle zugänglich sein sollten. Keine Registrierung, keine Premium-Pläne, keine versteckten Gebühren.",
    "faq_item_4_q": "Sind meine Ergebnisse privat?",
    "faq_item_4_a": "Absolut. Wir verfolgen Sie nicht, speichern Ihre Daten nicht und verwenden keine Cookies. Ihr Datenschutz ist unsere Priorität.",
    "faq_item_5_q": "Wie genau sind die Tests?",
    "faq_item_5_a": "Unsere Tests sind professionell und werden von Fotografen, Videografen und IT-Profis weltweit verwendet. Sie sind genauso genau wie kostenpflichtige Tools, die Hunderte von Euro kosten.",
    "faq_item_6_q": "Welche Geräte werden unterstützt?",
    "faq_item_6_a": "Alle Geräte mit einem modernen Webbrowser - Computer, Tablets, Telefone, Fernseher und mehr. Funktioniert auf Windows, Mac, Linux, iOS und Android.",
    "resource_faq_1_q": "Ist dieses Tool mit meinem Gerät kompatibel?",
    "resource_faq_1_a": "Ja! Unser Tool funktioniert auf allen modernen Geräten, einschließlich Smartphones, Tablets und Desktops. Es funktioniert in allen Browsern.",
    "resource_faq_2_q": "Kann ich das offline nutzen?",
    "resource_faq_2_a": "Ja! Sobald die Seite geladen ist, funktioniert das Tool offline. Wir unterstützen PWA-Installation für ein natives App-Erlebnis.",
    "resource_faq_3_q": "Wie kann ich dieses Tool teilen?",
    "resource_faq_3_a": "Klicken Sie auf die Schaltfläche \"Teilen\" oben auf der Seite, um direkt in sozialen Medien zu teilen, oder kopieren Sie den Link zum manuellen Teilen.",
    "privacy_intro": "Your privacy is important to us. This page explains how we handle your data.",
    "privacy_intro_full": "At TestaScreen, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring you have a positive experience on our website. This privacy policy explains our data practices, your rights, and how we comply with applicable regulations including the GDPR.",
    "privacy_data_collection": "Data Collection",
    "privacy_data_collection_text": "We do not collect personal data. We do not use cookies, trackers, or analytics services that identify you.",
    "privacy_how_it_works": "How It Works",
    "privacy_how_it_works_text": "All tests run directly in your browser. No data is sent to our servers. You have complete privacy and control.",
    "privacy_how_item_1": "All testing resources run entirely in your browser (client-side)",
    "privacy_how_item_2": "No information is transmitted to our servers or any third party",
    "privacy_how_item_3": "Results remain on your device only",
    "privacy_cookies": "Cookies & Local Storage",
    "privacy_cookies_text": "We do not use cookies or any form of local storage to track your behavior. We do not set any tracking cookies, analytics cookies, or marketing cookies.",
    "privacy_external_services": "External Services",
    "privacy_external_services_text": "We use Google Fonts for typography. While we strive to minimize data transfer, Google may receive requests from your browser to our server. For the strictest privacy, you may disable JavaScript for font loading or use a privacy-focused browser.",
    "privacy_gdpr_rights": "Your Rights Under GDPR",
    "privacy_gdpr_rights_text": "Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the following rights regarding your personal data:",
    "privacy_right_access": "Right of Access",
    "privacy_right_access_desc": "You have the right to obtain confirmation of whether your data is processed and to access that data.",
    "privacy_right_rectification": "Right of Rectification",
    "privacy_right_rectification_desc": "You can request correction of inaccurate personal data concerning you.",
    "privacy_right_erasure": "Right to Erasure (Right to be Forgotten)",
    "privacy_right_erasure_desc": "You can request deletion of your personal data in certain circumstances.",
    "privacy_right_portability": "Right to Data Portability",
    "privacy_right_portability_desc": "You have the right to receive your data in a structured, commonly used, machine-readable format.",
    "privacy_right_restrict": "Right to Restrict Processing",
    "privacy_right_restrict_desc": "You can request that we limit how we process your personal data.",
    "privacy_right_object": "Right to Object",
    "privacy_right_object_desc": "You have the right to object to processing of your data in certain circumstances.",
    "privacy_data_retention": "Data Retention",
    "privacy_data_retention_text": "Since we do not collect personal data, there is no data to retain. Any information generated by tools is stored only on your device and in your browser session, which is deleted when you close your browser.",
    "privacy_security": "Security",
    "privacy_security_text": "We take security seriously. All data processing occurs on your device. When visiting our website, we use HTTPS encryption to protect the integrity of communications between your browser and our server.",
    "privacy_third_parties": "Third-Party Links",
    "privacy_third_parties_text": "Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before providing any information.",
    "privacy_policy_changes": "Changes to This Policy",
    "privacy_policy_changes_text": "We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the \"last updated\" date.",
    "privacy_dpa": "Data Protection Authority Contact",
    "privacy_dpa_text": "If you believe we have violated your privacy rights or if you have concerns about how we handle your data, you have the right to lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.",
    "privacy_dpa_contact": "Data Protection Officer",
    "privacy_dpa_company_name": "TestaScreen",
    "privacy_contact_full_text": "For privacy inquiries, data access requests, or to exercise your rights under GDPR, please contact us:",
    "privacy_disclaimer": "This privacy policy is effective as of the date listed above. TestaScreen reserves the right to modify this policy at any time. Your continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of any changes.",
